dct_title_s: The new Europe / prepared at the request of the Savings Division by the U.S. Geological Survey ; engraved and printed by the U.S. Geological Survey. (Text)
dct_description_sm: On upper margin: "There are no boundaries to the future of the man who saves. On left and right margins: "War sayings stamps pay dividends to the thrifty." Text on verso: "Map makers for the people." "June 1919."
